WEBVTT

00:02:28.454 --> 00:02:30.488
and I can see my very hands.

00:02:31.026 --> 00:02:33.203
And in three, two, one,

00:02:33.227 --> 00:02:35.979
we're going to see an immersive
hologram appear,

00:02:36.003 --> 00:02:38.283
a very realistic hologram
appear in front of me,

00:02:38.307 --> 00:02:40.871
of our very glasses I'm wearing
on my head right now.

00:02:40.895 --> 00:02:43.736
